Package: FABLEDownscalR
Title: FABLE + DownscalR helpers for spatial downscaling workflows
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Clara Douzal
Maintainer: Clara Douzal <clara.douzal@unsdsn.org>
Description: Utilities to load and validate country inputs, build land-use transition
    matrices, rasterize the 50km grid, and produce standardized maps for FABLE and
    DownscalR downscaling workflows.
